## Variables CSS globales dans `index.css`

```css
/* src/styles/index.css */
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

@layer base {
  :root {
    --color-primary: #FF6B35;
    --color-surface: #F8F7F4;
    --color-dark: #1A1A2E;
  }

  html {
    @apply scroll-smooth;
  }

  body {
    @apply font-body text-dark bg-white antialiased;
  }

  h1, h2, h3, h4 {
    @apply font-heading;
  }

  /* Focus visible cohérent */
  *:focus-visible {
    @apply outline-none ring-2 ring-primary ring-offset-2;
  }
}

@layer utilities {
  /* Utilitaire section padding cohérent */
  .section-padding {
    @apply py-16 md:py-24;
  }

  /* Gradient text */
  .text-gradient {
    @apply bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-light bg-clip-text text-transparent;
  }
}
```

